OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA band of rain first thing,
OL,6,Foccasionally heavy with a risk of
OL,7,Fthunder, will clear away
OL,8,Fsoutheastwards during the morning.
OL,9,FSunny spells then follow but also
OL,10,Fisolated, possibly heavy showers. Any
OL,11,Fshowers easing during the afternoon.
OL,12,FWind easing. Cool.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA dry evening with sunny
OL,15,Fspells for many. However, showers will
OL,16,Fmove in from the northwest overnight,
OL,17,Fthese occasionally heavy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
